# Product Switcher — project conventions

Static fashion product switcher: `index.html` + `styles/main.css` + `scripts/*.js`, GSAP 3.12.7 CDN, vanilla JS IIFE. No build step required; `npm run dev` for local serve.

## Brand & visual language

- **Palette**: black nav bar (`#000`), white card (`#fff`, `border-radius: 40px`), accent gold `#C4A882` (logo accent + section 1).
- **Section colors** (`SECTION_COLORS`): `#C4A882`, `#C0C0C0`, `#D4C876` — keep in sync across switcher thumbs, fallback lerp, and nav-icon frames.
- **Typography**: `'Suisse Intl', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif`; nav 12px uppercase; product title/price 40px / 600 / -1.2px tracking.
- **Layout**: fixed 32px top nav; card inset 8px; central area 680×740px; bottom switcher pill (56px height, 23px radius).
- **Logo**: inline SVG in `#brandLogo` — hook arc, mark, bar, accent; tagline "Milano · Craft" below.

## BEM naming (strict)

Use block__element modifiers only. Existing blocks — do not rename without reason:

| Block | Elements |
|-------|----------|
| `top-nav` | `__group`, `__item`, `__logo`, `__logo-tagline` |
| `card` | (container) |
| `central-area` | video / `.fallback-color` |
| `info-left` | `__title`, `__details`, `__dimensions`, `__more` |
| `info-right` | `__price`, `__origin`, `__btn` |
| `switcher` | `__thumb`, `__inner` (+ `.active` on thumb) |

Logo SVG classes: `logo-hook`, `logo-mark`, `logo-mark-inner`, `logo-bar`, `logo-accent`, `logo-glow-group`.

## Product switcher behavior

- **3 sections** (`SECTION_COUNT = 3`): wheel scroll maps progress 0–1; thumbs jump to section midpoints `(index + 0.5) / 3`.
- **Video mode**: set `VIDEO_SRC` in `scripts/main.js` (patched by `setup-video.sh`); requires range-request server (`npx serve .`). Python `http.server` breaks `video.currentTime` seeking.
- **Fallback mode**: `VIDEO_SRC = null` — color lerp via `progressToColor()` on `.fallback-color`.
- **RAF loop** (`tick`): lerp `scrollProgress → targetProgress` (factor 0.15); update active section + switcher UI.

## Accessibility

- Nav: `<nav aria-label="Main navigation">`.
- Logo: `<button type="button">` with `aria-label="Brand logo — replay animation"`; replay on click, Enter, Space.
- Switcher: `role="tablist"`; thumbs `role="tab"`, `aria-selected`, `aria-label="Variant N"`.
- Decorative SVG/tagline: `aria-hidden="true"`.
- `:focus-visible` on logo (white outline); prefer keyboard parity with click handlers.
- `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)`: skip GSAP logo timeline; show final static state.

## Code style

- Vanilla JS in IIFE `'use strict'`; no frameworks unless explicitly requested.
- GSAP via CDN only: `gsap@3.12.7` — pin version on change.
- CSS in `styles/main.css`; JS split: `scripts/logo-animation.js` (GSAP logo), `scripts/main.js` (switcher/video).
- Load order: GSAP CDN → logo-animation.js → main.js.
- Comments in English for FFmpeg/setup blocks; user-facing copy may stay English (fashion retail tone).

## Do not

- Add API keys, analytics, or backend without explicit request.
- Break wheel-scroll ↔ video/fallback sync or thumb active state.
- Use `python -m http.server` for video testing (documented limitation).
